Paper: hep-th/0205313

Date: 2002-05-30

Title: Classical Radiation of a Finite Number of Photons

Authors: L. Stodolsky

Comments: 8 pages, 1 figure

Journal-ref: Acta Phys.Polon. B33 (2002) 2659

Under certain conditions the number of photons radiated classically by acharged particle following a prescribed trajectory can be finite. Aninteresting formula for this number is presented and discussed.